Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.78,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind whispers to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.71,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's delicious. It's beyond delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I have to make sense of everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.57,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Menma here?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.03,0:00:18.83,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she can't go to heaven because she's clinging to some worldly regret.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.55,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds about right. {timing check}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.38,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.36,0:00:28.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.56,0:00:30.63,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Menma I know is always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.68,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}smiling{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.22,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Who could like that ugly...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always wanted to apologize to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.56,0:00:54.19,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it goes beyond ordinary contrition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.19,0:00:56.28,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that much for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.80,0:01:08.50,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Maybe that's my wish: to have you go to school.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.74,0:01:11.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,School.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,-OP-
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you going to school?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.81,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have to explain.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Before this you were yelling at me to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.41,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Before is before,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,but now go forth before you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.29,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.97,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.65,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But you look so grim...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm all set! {lit. Nothing left to brush/polish}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.51,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.50,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you want right?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.62,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You can rely on me a bit too you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.62,0:04:02.11,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to let you go to heaven.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.73,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Has Jintan's mom gone to heaven?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.72,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what going to heaven is like.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.13,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in control of myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. My heart is empty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.81,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Empty... empty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.54,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,It's impressive how someone can act like it's no big deal coming to school after that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.55,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I know right. Are you talking about that first year from class 3?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.58,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Her name's Naruko Anjou.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.82,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.19,Default,Bear,0000,0000,0000,,Anjou.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.10,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,See? Looks like it was true after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anjou?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.64,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Anjou?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This has been really anticlimactic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are a few people who have noticed me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's that guy who's never showed up before. {fucking Sherlock}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way! She was called to the principal's office?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.91,Default,Grirl2,0000,0000,0000,,Naruko really screwed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.90,Default,Grirl2,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think going to a love hotel is such a big deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Anjou's got me beat by a long shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.78,0:05:46.86,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this I feel like I psyched myself up for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.28,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from the PTA saw her.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she was with some old guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.20,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You think he was paying her?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.42,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.28,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone back to their seat.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.63,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Class is starting.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.98,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a seat too Anjou.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.82,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Open up your books...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.97,Default,Whore1,0000,0000,0000,,You messed up bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.58,0:06:37.32,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the sentiment of this story's narrator
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.12,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,is on several occasions tinged with rage.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.75,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,First and foremost is his anger at that man and his wife's betrayal.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.77,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm amazed she's taking notes at a time like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.40,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's always been that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not smart. She learns slowly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Try as she might...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.98,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,Anjou's really out there.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.57,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll let you do her if you ask.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.57,0:07:03.63,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,"...Sense of self-respect as a man has been gravely injured."
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.91,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anjou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.80,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Second is his anger at himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.92,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,The contents of the letter allude to this fact.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.51,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,"To assert my dominance as both a man and a husband before him..."{No clue where these go}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll let you do her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.73,0:07:30.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did he pay her?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.05,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.15,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.66,0:07:54.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the guy who hasn't showed up to school in a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to school except for the opening ceremony and the first week of classes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.48,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look to you? Ain't I a sight to see?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"Ain't I?"
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What language is that? {no hicks in glorious Nippon}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.92,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Uh... What? Could you be...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.30,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.51,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.65,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I can give her a booty call any time, anywhere. {not trollin, this is what he said}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.55,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all really making a big deal out of some love hotel?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.01,0:08:21.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it be obvious looking at her that she's been to one a time or two?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.70,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,She's got that love hotel look to her!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.10,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.10,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.71,0:08:29.19,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say this once.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.88,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,She'd never take money for sex.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.87,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, she's a Capricorn and has blood-type A.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.18,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,She's never gone out on a limb, she's serious to a fault, and had this pissed off look when she wore glasses.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.37,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,She's got tons of stuff and she's a neat freak... {timing check}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.43,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,She's collected tiny things since she was little.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.86,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,And her glasses... Damn, what a lame chick....
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.12,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.13,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Get your bag.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.88,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Lets get out of here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.94,0:08:57.85,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.19,Default,Whore,0000,0000,0000,,Naruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.63,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,"Look at me."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.73,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like an exhibitionist.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.32,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.83,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,But... Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.82,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You covered for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.38,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.41,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have "that love hotel look"!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.63,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I've really never gone to a love hotel.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.39,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even been inside one.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.72,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.63,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "Yeah, sure"?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.06,0:09:39.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, just head home. Your mom's probably worried about you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.62,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going? Your house is this way.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.10,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.74,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,The school has probably already called my home.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.40,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be angry at me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.35,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,She'd never let something like this go.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.44,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Anjou.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.96,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's not right...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.44,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean you're staying over?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.96,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be until things calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.18,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Until things calm down?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.12,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know that this place is my castle,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,and it's soaked up various manly fluids including but not limited to sweat and tears.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.02,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,We all built it together.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.27,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's proof. I carved out that Hamtaro.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.06,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hamtaro?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.03,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It looks more like a sausage than a ham.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.48,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start off by cleaning up since that man juice stinks so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.48,0:10:42.68,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,H-h-h-hey, don't touch those!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.12,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What the? This is rotten!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.45,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about her?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she stays over she should tell her mom about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.65,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise there'll be an uproar.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.87,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so timid.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.30,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,She always huddled in Menma's shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.83,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.65,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Menma now?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.84,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,She's not around.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.12,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.36,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we go check out her house?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.66,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,We might get an idea about her wish that way.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to grant my wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.84,0:11:24.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.82,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better if Menma came with us?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.95,0:11:34.01,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but, wouldn't it be kind of awkward to say
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.54,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, let's go to Menma's house", when she's right there?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.20,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were that good at reading people's feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.64,0:11:45.73,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I did become a level 5 Shaman while I was in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.44,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Those exist?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.44,0:11:51.64,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Great, now that that's settled, let's text Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.66,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, what's his number...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.19,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? He's so cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.80,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That's how college-prep schools are.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.80,0:12:06.49,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. I'd thought that no one had changed at all after I saw everyone again.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.03,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the case. People do change, little by little.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.72,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we shouldn't go to Menma's house after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.83,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.97,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it, we've never even gone to her house to play before.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.97,0:12:26.59,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Menma's dad was one scary guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.86,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe this is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.40,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I want to light an incense stick for Menma.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.43,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.39,0:12:46.41,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but think about how Menma's mom will react when she sees us.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.80,0:12:53.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe everyone came here. Meiko would be so happy too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Now come in, come in.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Could you say hello to Meiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's bothering me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Menma's dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.88,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've known that all along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This is Meiko's room. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsurumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.21,0:13:53.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Minako wants you to give this to Matsuyuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.56,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.42,0:14:00.00,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same class. She should just give it to him herself.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.73,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.32,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so high and mighty.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.68,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look down on me just because you're always by his side.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.78,0:14:13.13,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it! You like Matsuyuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.82,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.82,0:14:15.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.57,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.37,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.25,Default,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.95,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Heading home? Be careful.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.81,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,There have been shady people around these parts lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.48,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,People always get envious of you like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.19,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.19,0:15:03.25,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'd be freed of all my worries the instant I sent out photos of you cross-dressing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.41,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.76,0:15:09.38,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, apparently Yadomi and the others are going to Menma's house.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.38,0:15:13.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so they're all taking what Yadomi said seriously.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.22,0:15:18.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can leave the past behind them.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.56,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You least of all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.31,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.84,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally being honest.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.84,0:15:29.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get anything past you if I tried anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.75,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He pisses me off.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.53,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.02,0:15:37.53,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Be it the school I go to, or my overall standing,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.50,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,right now I'm far above him in every way.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.01,0:15:45.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still getting caught up in his pace like back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He even spoke Menma's name.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.64,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How long does he plan to make a fool out of everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,On that day..
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.64,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If only he hadn't told everyone to gather at the secret fort.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.38,0:16:04.48,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Menma call us that day?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.70,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Menma gave me a call.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,She called?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.16,0:16:16.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's right. She wanted to talk about something that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.52,0:16:20.76,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said she had something she wanted to talk about, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.97,0:16:31.10,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she'd hand over Menma's diary that easily.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.94,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What a great mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.54,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't that depressing?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.22,0:16:46.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My husband told me I couldn't stay obsessed with Meiko forever, so he cleaned up this room.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.45,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Meiko's things are in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.07,0:16:57.77,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What else can they do? Seeing her things will only make it harder for them.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.90,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If they see...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.92,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how a mother feels,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.92,0:17:07.19,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,but I think having a child must be an extremely heavy burden in a lot of way.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.01,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that with a straight face?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.17,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should head home.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.01,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm worried about my parents or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.18,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something I had to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.17,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.17,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,She's not being honest with herself.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.17,0:17:31.67,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, we got the diary so let's head back to the secret fort and read it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Could that wait a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.66,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of cooking dinner tonight,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.35,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,and I haven't washed the plates from this morning, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.14,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.66,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go ahead and...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.81,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't read it without me. Don't do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.76,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... all alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.74,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing will only make it harder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.28,0:18:04.92,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then would it have been better not to have seen Menma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.19,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.91,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Jintan! How was school?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.93,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've already seen her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.44,0:18:22.43,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only harder...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.60,0:18:29.08,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So you know, I sort of went with the flow and went to see your mom today...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.33,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Confiscated!	{she combines the words for 'confiscated' bosshuu and 'dustshoot' dasutoshuuto into a cute way of saying 'removed'}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.33,0:18:30.73,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.04,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Confiscated! Confiscated!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.14,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,CONFISCATED!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.21,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.28,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.89,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.98,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean why?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.24,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.77,0:18:55.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that my mom will remember me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting my mom
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.78,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,through lots and lots of sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.43,0:19:10.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make her any more sad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.58,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make her remember me anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.22,0:19:17.59,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You may not want her to remember you, but that's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.18,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.18,0:19:18.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care that it's impossible!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only a little bit,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.35,0:19:25.62,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mom to forget about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.68,0:19:35.64,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right. You said yourself that you'd be happy if we all remembered you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.94,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.63,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You're always worrying about others like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.15,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Think about yourself a little more!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude pisses me off!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.73,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You laugh it off even when you're hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.68,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,When you cry it's only for other people.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.67,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I yelling like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.37,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.34,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.68,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.79,0:20:06.01,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nosebleed!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.68,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Umm, umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.78,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Here, stuff this tissue inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.78,0:20:12.81,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.13,0:20:12.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Tissue!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.98,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,And then lie down facing up!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.55,0:20:21.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That way it'll get better.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.30,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.77,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.00,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This late?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.21,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.18,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.95,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really. What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.01,0:20:59.49,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi? What are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.96,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Didn't you go home?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.87,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,And what about the way you're dressed?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I had some blood backed up in my nose already.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.61,0:21:11.61,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it's not because you were turning me on...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.16,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.16,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! Pervert!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.21,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Pervy-scurvy one-touchy!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.44,0:21:21.92,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have no doubts. She's definitely a virgin.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.51,0:22:59.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ghost of a mother-in-law tortured to death by her inhuman family strikes back!{\i0}
