Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.38,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon pages and pages of entries
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.79,0:01:29.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,We've put down all our emotions
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.84,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I've hit a writer's block
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to finish this page anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.97,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting a bookmark in my diary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.64,0:01:45.06,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.23,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to our secret place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.78,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.83,0:02:02.37,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.50,0:02:05.58,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,With cider in my right hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.58,0:02:10.04,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,My other hand helps me search for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.80,0:02:14.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to come find me way back when
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.42,0:02:17.84,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to demand me of so much more
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.84,0:02:24.64,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both still standing right by my side
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.02,0:02:32.44,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.65,0:02:40.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something off with me
