Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:53.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}aa hanabi ga yozora kirei ni saite chotto setsunaku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:22:00.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}aa kaze ga jikan to tomo ni nagareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:07.73,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ureshikute tanoshikute bouken mo iro iro shita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:14.40,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:21.95,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kimi to natsu no owari shourai no yume ookina kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:29.04,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}jyuunen no ato hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:36.26,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou" sakendeita koto shitetayo
