Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:52.93,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)\an8}saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:53.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks blossomed heartrendingly beautiful across the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:22:00.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,and time passed as swiftly as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.61,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We met in an unexpected moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:42.29,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.96,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's walk home together."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:07.73,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We shared so many happy times and thrilling adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:14.40,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,together in our secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:21.95,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:29.04,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:36.26,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:39.05,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it must've been painful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:43.31,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:52.93,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}But those are my best memories.
